Package com.roscopeco.moxy.impl.asm

Interface ASMMockSupport


  • public interface ASMMockSupport
    All mocks implement this interface. It (ab)uses default methods to allow us to do less bytecode generation. Don't implement this yourself, it's only public because it needs to be visible to subclasses.
    Author:
    Ross Bamford <roscopeco AT gmail DOT com>
